*Sladoled* je najomiljeniji desert u ovom lokalu. (Ice cream is the most beloved desert in this restaurant.)

Moj sin je danas pojeo tri kugle *sladoleda*. (My son ate three scoops of ice cream today.)

Kupila sam čokoladni *sladoled* za dezert. (I bought a chocolate ice cream for dessert.)

Moj brat je kupio *sladoled* za svoju nećakinju. (My brother bought an ice cream for his niece.)

Moja ćerka voli da jede *sladoled* uz crveni sos. (My daughter likes to eat ice cream with red sauce.)